\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces QCDI (Quality-Calibration Degradation Index) for all methods, sorted descending. Color bands indicate taxonomy class. D+QCTS (green star) is the only post-hoc method in the Quality-Aware zone.}}{9}{figure.1}\protected@file@percent }
